Package com.flipkart.dao

Interface FlipFitAdminDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitAdminDAOImpl
public interface FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
Interface for FlipFit Admin Data Access Object (DAO) operations. Provides methods to handle admin functionalities related to gym owners and centres.
